The Audit and Logging module records critical user actions, system activities, and transaction events to ensure accountability and traceability. It supports security monitoring, compliance reporting, and incident investigation by maintaining a reliable audit trail across the application.
üîπ Overall System Behavior
Each module operates independently to ensure flexibility and maintainability; however, all modules are governed by a centralized security and architectural framework. This unified design ensures system consistency, scalability, and seamless integration across functional areas.
